modDescription:
A trash can that can be used to store and delete unwanted items. Place it on the ground like a normal block. Interacting with the top of the trash can will open the container. To delete the items, interact with the base (the metal area). You will pick up the container. When you place it on the ground it will be empty again.

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/Alter-s09/Modlets/tree/main/Alter_TrashBin)**
